---
<Layout title="Selling by Auction in Brisbane: How It Works and What to Expect | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Auction is a significant sales method across Brisbane's inner east. Here is what the process looks like from the vendor's side, including Queensland rules, reserve prices, and what happens on the day." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
